Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_disabl...ew_propagation(25.10)    timing_disabl...ew_propagation(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_retime_clock_path_slew_propagation

Syntax
       timing_disable_retime_clock_path_slew_propagation

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       When  set  to true, path based analysis is performed on data paths only
       and the clock segments are not considered.

       When set to false, analysis is performed on both data and clock paths.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

